Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
edu.sjsu.assignment4.Appointment
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Appointment>
Direct Known Subclasses:
DailyAppointment, MonthlyAppointment, OnetimeAppointment
public abstract class Appointment extends Object implements Comparable<Appointment>
Appointment is an abstract class containing the basic properties of an appointment. Subclasses must overload occursOn()

    • compareTo

      public int compareTo(Appointment appointment)
      compareTo overrides compareTo from Comparable to order Appointments first by startDate, then by endDate, then by description. If all three match, the Appointments are equal
      Specified by:
      compareTo in interface Comparable<Appointment>
      Parameters:
      appointment - Appointment for the right hand side of the comparison
      Returns:
      0 if equal, positive if this should be before appointment, negative if this should be after appointment
